995b2510-7b8f-49a1-9a12-77cb45d471ab.name: Change of Major
995b2510-7b8f-49a1-9a12-77cb45d471ab.description: Students can request a change of major or a program change through a form that can be embedded to and started from the University’s website. After the student submits the form, the academic advisor receives a notification to review the request. If the request is approved, the Registrar is informed to update the Student Information System.
